    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've talked to people. doctors, neighbors... they all say the same thing, \"just hang in there\" or \"be patient.\" but it doesn't feel patient, it feels like being trapped. it feels like being forced to watch a slow, painful decline with no say in the matter. i just wish i had some kind of agency, you know? some way to decide when the story is actually over instead of just letting it drag on.",
